File::MetaInfo - A simple keyword indexing and searching system for files.
Brief and Dirty Instructions
============================

For now there is no Makefile.PL file. I need help do do this a Bundle.

Collecting Meta-Data (Indexing)
-------------------------------

go to scripts directory
   1. edit setenv.sh 
      Edit at least the FILEMETAINFO_BASEDIR to match your installation directory
   2. run setenv.sh
   3. run setup.sh
      This will create the db and register the Extract modules and create the Nautilus Scripts
   4. run MetaInfoUpdateDB BASEDIR
      BASEDIR is the directory you want to scan for indexing

